Package civitas.celestis.util.grid

Interface Grid<V,G extends Grid<V,G>>

Type Parameters:
V - The type of value to contain in this grid
G - This grid (the result of various operations)
All Superinterfaces:
Iterable<V>
All Known Subinterfaces:
Matrix<N,M>
All Known Implementing Classes:
DoubleMatrix, LongMatrix
public interface Grid<V,G extends Grid<V,G>> extends Iterable<V>
A two-dimensional grid of objects.
